</a>. This video card has 3 DisplayPorts and 2 HDMI ports.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>What really wraps up this bundle well is a 4-year warranty.&nbsp; This is uncommon, and a nice thing to see.&nbsp; Instead of a standard 3-year warranty GIGABYTE gives you one more year of protection for free.&nbsp; To enjoy this 4-year warranty you must register on the website within 30 days of purchase.</p>', 9),
