rong>Dolby Atmos®</strong></h3><p>Astonishing clarity, richness and depth of sound to create a 3D sound field - enveloping you in the atmosphere.</p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:600px;\"><img src=\"https://www.panasonic.com/content/dam/pim/vn/en/TH/TH-65J/TH-65JX750V/ast-1286396.jpg.pub.thumb.644.644.jpg\" alt=\"Dolby Atmos®\"></figure><h2 style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong>Specs</strong></h2><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:81.37%;\"><img src=\"https://www.panasonic.com/content/dam/pim/vn/en/TH/TH-65J/TH-65JX750V/ast-1286447.png.pub.thumb.644.644.png\" alt=\"Photo of TH-65JX750V 65 inch, LED LCD, 4K HDR Android TV\"></figure>',12),
