ip case, which is exclusive to China. The watch is expected to be released in Japan and Asia in November 2021 (though a delay is possible), with other regions to follow.</p><p>Updates: The GM-2100MG-1AJR will be released in December 2021 in Japan for 37,400 yen. Casio Europe released the GM-2100MG-1AER (299 euros) online on December 6 <a href=\"https://www.g-shock.eu/de/uhren/limited/gm-2100mg-1aer/\"><u>at www.g-shock.eu</u></a>. The GM-2100MG-1A is also a December release throughout Asia. The GM-2100MG-1AER is also listed as coming soon at G-Shock U.K. with a price of £289.</p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/GM-2100MG-1A-LARGE.jpg\" alt=\"G-Shock GM-2100MG-1A The Moon Hi-Res Image\"></figure><p style=\"text-align:center;\"><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/sch/i.html?_from=R40&amp;_trksid=p2380057.m570.l1313&amp;_nkw=GM-2100MG-1AJR&amp;_sacat=0&amp;mkrid=711-53200-19255-0&amp;siteid=0&amp;mkcid=1&amp;campid=5337710300&amp;toolid=11800&amp;mkevt=1\"><strong>GM-2100MG-1AJR (JP) on eBay</strong></a></p><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/GM-2100MG-1A-CASE-BACK.jpg\" alt=\"G-Shock GM-2100MG-1A Moon Case Back\"></figure><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/GM-2100MG-1A-MOON-03.jpg\" alt=\"G-Shock GM-2100MG-1A Moon-Themed Watch\"></figure><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/GM-2100MG-1AJR-BOX-680x453.jpg\" alt=\"G-Shock GM-2100MG-1A Case and Box\"></figure><figure class=\"image\"><img src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/GM-2100MG-1A.jpg\" alt=\"G-Shock GM-2100MG-1A The Moon\"></figure>', 6),
